    //                     + sum of (1 - strategy[i]) * prices[i] for next halfK elements
    // So the total change is: sum of (-strategy[i] * prices[i]) for first halfK
    //                        + sum of (1 - strategy[i]) * prices[i] for next halfK
    // Which can be rewritten as: sum of (prices[i] * (1 - strategy[i])) for next halfK
    //                           - sum of (prices[i] * strategy[i]) for first halfK

