    // The window is from i to i + k - 1
    // The first half is i to i + halfK - 1, set to 0
    // The second half is i + halfK to i + k - 1, set to 1

    // The profit change for a window starting at i is:
    // (sum of 0 - original strategy in first half) + (sum of prices - original strategy in second half)
    // = -sum(strategy[j] * prices[j] for j in first half) + sum((1 - strategy[j]) * prices[j] for j in second half)

